Create the same CPU subsystem floorplan in FC:
- Die area: {0 0 800 800}
- Core area: {15 15 785 785}
- Place `sram_cache` at coordinates {50 50}, orientation R0
- Place `sram_buffer` at coordinates {400 50}, orientation R0
- Add macro keepout halo of 15um to `sram_cache`
- Add macro keepout halo of 15um to `sram_buffer`
- Create hard placement blockage at {{380 380} {420 420}}
- Run `check_floorplan` and `report_floorplan`
